WEBVTT

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:31.120
people thought I was the maid.

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:34.696
I was even treated like a prostitute

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:39.240
just because I was walking alone
on the beach with European friends.

00:02:39.760 --> 00:02:41.256
And many times,

00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:45.856
visiting my grandma or friends
in upper class buildings,

00:02:45.880 --> 00:02:50.816
I was invited not to use
the main elevator.

00:02:50.840 --> 00:02:53.216
Because in the end,

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:55.936
with this color and this hair,

00:02:55.960 --> 00:02:58.880
I cannot belong to some places.